title: Cannot include python torch/csrc/utils/python_numbers.h in extension
body_html:
When I include torch/csrc/utils/python_numbers.h, compilation will fail as it indirectly includes
torch/csrc/jit/generated/aten_interned_strings.h which is not in torch/lib/includes.
This is on master from today on Linux.

My main use case was adding an IntList pybind converter.

body:
When I include `torch/csrc/utils/python_numbers.h`, compilation will fail as it indirectly includes
`torch/csrc/jit/generated/aten_interned_strings.h` which is not in `torch/lib/includes`.
This is on master from today on Linux.

My main use case was adding an IntList pybind converter.
